Yesterday in Cancun, the UN proposed a plan to renew the lighting of households, trade and industry in 100 countries with a view to reducing greenhouse gas (FCKW) which corresponds to nearly one third of the additional reduction that needs to be achieved in order to stabilise the Earth's climate by 2020.
